271
00:17:19,521 --> 00:17:20,929
Sim, peixe.

272
00:17:20,930 --> 00:17:22,823
Sei como acontece.

273
00:17:23,129 --> 00:17:24,843
<i>Caldo de pescado.</i>

274
00:17:26,701 --> 00:17:30,111
<i>Eso es lo que estaba comiendo,
